&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 2 Full Time Permanent Position&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Rota Porter position isa full timecontract, this rotates through a 20 person rota, which covers various shift, such as early mornings, evenings, Night shift.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Also whilst on float Shifts you may pick up areas to cover such as the Post room, Coordinating and Clinical waste and E.D Porters.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The job entails Transporting patients through the hospital by the means of Bed stretcher and wheelchair. Collecting patient notes, units of blood and other items, also Mortuary duties and Emergency Helmed evacuations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
